<p class="">Is it a quarter of 145,000?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ab4567e6-42fd-4ddc-aa27-3f87c63bcfd4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-03-08/debates/5e5993a5-6193-479f-a64a-2a1fcd4f2af4/MrJohnDugdaleSStatement#contribution-ab4567e6-42fd-4ddc-aa27-3f87c63bcfd4">
