        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d2c2b253-004f-4c57-b4ee-d9605504b533">
                Mr. J. Langford-Holt  (Shrewsbury)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d2c2b253-004f-4c57-b4ee-d9605504b533" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-03-08/debates/5e5993a5-6193-479f-a64a-2a1fcd4f2af4/MrJohnDugdaleSStatement#contribution-d2c2b253-004f-4c57-b4ee-d9605504b533">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Before the hon. Gentleman sits down, may I ask him a question? In reply to the right hon. Member for Woodford (Mr. Churchill) he pointed out that naval aviation was at least one-third or one-quarter of the whole of the Navy. In a speech of three quarters of an hour, he devoted approximately 40 seconds to naval aviation. Do we really understand that is all he is going to say on that question?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d2c2b253-004f-4c57-b4ee-d9605504b533" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-03-08/debates/5e5993a5-6193-479f-a64a-2a1fcd4f2af4/MrJohnDugdaleSStatement#contribution-d2c2b253-004f-4c57-b4ee-d9605504b533">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

