            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c848e2c9-9dfa-4371-9211-065b5c4b3d71" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
