<p class="">The "J" class did not have turrets.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f8acd788-0b65-42c3-b1b6-30901d1dc816" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
