<p class="">That would not be too bad, either.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-969904d6-bc12-4de8-90cb-d9dbb5bc3f93" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
