                Lieut.-Commander Gurney Braithwaite  (Holderness)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dc504d68-8f4b-4a59-85c0-fdd313df87a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
