                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I would remind the hon. and gallant Gentleman that the late H. G. Wells has proved himself so far a staggeringly accurate prophet.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5e69c7bf-8f02-4ce3-8832-e4b6995e7bb7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-03-08/debates/5e5993a5-6193-479f-a64a-2a1fcd4f2af4/MrJohnDugdaleSStatement#contribution-5e69c7bf-8f02-4ce3-8832-e4b6995e7bb7">
