                Mr. Foot
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8dc16d79-9246-4ea8-92cc-1b8bec372f05" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-03-08/debates/5e5993a5-6193-479f-a64a-2a1fcd4f2af4/MrJohnDugdaleSStatement#contribution-8dc16d79-9246-4ea8-92cc-1b8bec372f05">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of Order. Is it not a great discourtesy, to the House that the Leader of the Opposition, who has made this point, should not be present to hear the reply?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8dc16d79-9246-4ea8-92cc-1b8bec372f05" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
