                Mr. Maclay
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cbf1d4cf-1fba-4d90-a93e-5bae63db15c2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
